  contents: ["Important information is stored in your account on the #{EnrollRegistry[:enroll_app].setting(:short_name).item} website.  If you don’t have an account already, you can create one by going to <a href='www.DCHealthLink.com'>#{Settings.site.website_name}</a>. You can get help with logging in or creating an account by calling #{EnrollRegistry[:enroll_app].setting(:short_name).item} Customer Service toll-free <br>at 1-855-532-5465."],
    heading: 'Your Secure User Account', sub_heading: ''} %>
